/span><span class=\"bp\">=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∑</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">∈</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Finset</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">range</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">m</span><span class=\"o\">,</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">f</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">length</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"gr\">sorry</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Although still some problem with syntax...</p>",
